# Order of the Awakened v3
Bonus Disciplines		KEY:Order of the Awakened ~ Bonus Disciplines	BONUS:VAR|POOL_Awakened_Discipline|2	CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 1st level, you learn two additional psionic disciplines of your choice. They must be chosen from among the Awakened disciplines.	
Awakened Talent		KEY:Order of the Awakened ~ Awakened Talent		CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 1st level, you gain proficiency with two of the following skills of your choice: Animal Handling, Deception, Insight, Intimidation, Investigation, Perception, and Persuasion.	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Awakened Skill|2
Psionic Investigation	KEY:Order of the Awakened ~ Psionic Investigation	CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Starting at 3rd level, you can focus your mind to read the psionic imprint left on an object. If you hold an object and concentrate on it for 10 minutes (as if concentrating on a psionic discipline), you learn a few basic facts about it. You gain a mental image from the object's point of view, showing the last creature to hold the object within the past 24 hours. You also learn of any events that have occurred within 20 feet of the object within the past hour. The events you perceive unfold from the object's perspective. You see and hear such events as if you were there, but can't use other senses. Additionally, you can embed an intangible psionic sensor within the object. For the next 24 hours, you can use an action to learn the object's location relative to you (its distance and direction) and to look at the object's surroundings from its point of view as if you were there. This perception lasts until the start of your next turn. Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a short or long rest.
Psionic Surge		KEY:Order of the Awakened ~ Psionic Surge			CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Starting at 6th level, you can overload your psychic focus to batter down an opponent's defenses. You can impose disadvantage on a target's saving throw against a discipline or talent you use, but at the cost of using your psychic focus. Your psychic focus immediately ends if it's active, and you can't use it until you finish a short or long rest. You can't use this feature if you can't use your psychic focus.
Spectral Form		KEY:Order of the Awakened ~ Spectral Form			CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 14th level, you gain the ability to become a ghostly figure of psionic energy. As an action, you can transform into a transparent, ghostly version of yourself. While in this form, you have resistance to all damage, move at half speed, and can pass through objects and creatures while moving but can't willingly end your movement in their spaces. The form lasts for 10 minutes or until you use an action to end it. Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.

# Order of the Immortal v3
Bonus Disciplines		KEY:Order of the Immortal ~ Bonus Disciplines				BONUS:VAR|POOL_Immortal_Discipline|2	CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 1st level, you learn two additional psionic disciplines of your choice. They must be chosen from among the Immortal disciplines.
Immortal Durability	KEY:Order of the Immortal ~ Immortal Durability			CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Starting at 1st level, your hit point maximum increases by 1 per mystic level. In addition, while you aren't wearing armor or wielding a shield, your base AC equals 10 + your Dexterity modifier + your Constitution modifier.	BONUS:HP|CURRENTMAX|MysticLVL
Psionic Resilience	KEY:Order of the Immortal ~ Psionic Resilience			CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Starting at 3rd level, your psionic energy grants you extraordinary fortitude. At the start of each of your turns, you gain temporary hit points equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of 0) if you have at least 1 hit point.
Surge of Health		KEY:Order of the Immortal ~ Surge of Health			CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Starting at 6th level, you can draw on your psychic focus to escape death's grasp. As a reaction when you take damage, you can halve that damage against you. Your psychic focus immediately ends if it's active, and you can't use it until you finish a short or long rest. You can't use this feature if you can't use your psychic focus.
Immortal Will		KEY:Order of the Immortal ~ Immortal Will				CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Starting at 14th level, you can draw on your reserves of psionic power to survive beyond death. At the end of your turn while at 0 hit points, you can spend 5 psi points to immediately regain a number of hit points equal to your mystic level + your Constitution modifier.

# Order of the Nomad v3
Bonus Disciplines			KEY:Order of the Nomad ~ Bonus Disciplines			BONUS:VAR|POOL_Nomad_Discipline|2	CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 1st level, you learn two additional psionic disciplines of your choice. They must be chosen from among the Nomad disciplines.
Breadth of Knowledge		KEY:Order of the Nomad ~ Breadth of Knowledge		CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 1st level, you gain the ability to extend your knowledge. When you finish a long rest, you gain two proficiencies of your choice: two tools, two skills, or one of each. You can replace one or both of these selections with languages. This benefit lasts until you finish a long rest.
Memory of One Thousand Steps	KEY:Order of the Nomad ~ Memory of One Thousand Steps	CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 3rd level, you gain the ability to use psionics to recall your steps. As a reaction when you are hit by an attack, you can teleport to an unoccupied space that you occupied since the start of your last turn, and the attack misses you. Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a short or long rest.
Superior Teleportation		KEY:Order of the Nomad ~ Superior Teleportation		CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 6th level, you gain a superior talent for teleportation. When you use a psionic discipline to teleport any distance, you can increase that distance by up to 10 feet.
Effortless Journey		KEY:Order of the Nomad ~ Effortless Journey		CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Starting at 14th level, your mind can mystically move your body. Once on each of your turns, you can forfeit up to 30 feet of your movement to teleport the distance you forfeited. You must teleport to an unoccupied space you can see.

# Order of the Soul Knife v3
Martial Training		KEY:Order of the Soul Knife ~ Martial Training			CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:At 1st level, you gain proficiency with medium armor and martial weapons.	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|TYPE=WeaponProfMartial|TYPE=ArmorProfMedium
Soul Knife			KEY:Order of the Soul Knife ~ Soul Knife				CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Starting at 1st level, you gain the ability to manifest a blade of psychic energy. As a bonus action, you create scintillating knives of energy that project from both of your fists. You can't hold anything in your hands while manifesting these blades. You can dismiss them as a bonus action. For you, a soul knife is a martial melee weapon with the light and finesse properties. It deals 1d8 psychic damage on a hit. As a bonus action, you can prepare to use the blades to parry; you gain a +2 bonus to AC until the start of your next turn or until you are incapacitated.
Hone the Blade		KEY:Order of the Soul Knife ~ Hone the Blade			CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Starting at 3rd level, you can spend psi points to augment your soul knife's attack rolls and damage. You gain a bonus to attack and damage rolls with your soul knives depending on the number of psi points spent, as shown on the table below. This bonus lasts for 10 minutes. Psi Points Attack and Damage Bonus ; 2 +1; 5 +2; 7 +4
Consumptive Knife		KEY:Order of the Soul Knife ~ Consumptive Knife			CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Starting at 6th level, whenever you slay an enemy creature with a soul knife attack, you immediately regain 2 psi points.
Phantom Knife		KEY:Order of the Soul Knife ~ Phantom Knife			CATEGORY:Special Ability	SORTKEY:Class Mystic 2c	TYPE:Mystic Class Feature.SpecialQuality	SOURCEPAGE:p.	DESC:Starting at 14th level, you can make an attack that phases through most defenses. As an action, you can make one attack with your soul knife. Treat the target's AC as 10 against this attack, regardless of the target's actual AC.

